{"tid":1281380,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港需要獨立民調","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:58:14.000Z","uid":270374,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70a3ed5c82ef179cec9b2fb78175083e0975fa59","tid":1281380,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"全文﹕<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190701/20717364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717364&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=c4706a55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717364&h=78f3b024\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190701/20717364</a><br />\n<br />\n有28年歷史的香港大學民意研究計劃結束，今日起轉做獨立機構「香港民意研究所」，依靠公民捐款維持運作。香港民研4月底宣佈，要一次過籌募600萬元起動基金，才可順利過渡，可惜至今僅籌到2萬餘元，香港民研主席鍾庭耀未有明言「讓路」予反惡法運動，只說社會有其他事「更需要資源」，今需重啟眾籌，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望公民社會支持，令特首民望等民調毋須「斷纜」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n「香港民意研究所」捐款網址： <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation%20%20&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=ab33d92c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation  </a>"},{"pid":"b069b6e0d5ef29d67c3376c5c2b981ef06415e24","tid":1281380,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f83a71d99b0523de832a7348c7b53a033a9d2905","tid":1281380,"uid":270374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌進度不理想，鍾庭耀承認，除非在三、四天內收到足夠捐款，否則原來每兩周發佈一次的特首民調，今個7月勢將「斷纜」</span></span>"},{"pid":"3113eb11143d4290a5096dc0362efb014a99ef6c","tid":1281380,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足，我地極需要客觀民調去幫手打輿論戰，<br />\n盡力保護前線 ! <br />\n唔該，幫手推啦 !!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d22a6777311de4b5306257a76d57efb296cb2e1f","tid":1281380,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"123cb3fb4b1bb3ec5f8116e3852ee799afbffeab","tid":1281380,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078d58f2590ca527edb59f407744adf87e8f774d","tid":1281380,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e03da1e9eb9c9ac2a875254acac72ea833e12937","tid":1281380,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}